{"tid":1672699,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太陽城集團主席周焯華 入稟向中滔環保追1.8億","createTime":"2019-10-24T09:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T16:51:05.000Z","uid":185631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"40cfddc937963991a70a52932eba023db8cfe22d","tid":1672699,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"太陽城集團主席周焯華，指去年向上市公司中滔環保借出貸款，合共1.8億元，並由中滔的董事徐湛滔任擔保人，惟中滔環保只清還部份利息。周昨（23日）入稟高等法院，循民事途經向中滔環保追討欠款。<br />\n<br />\n原告為周焯華，被告為中滔環保集團有限公司和中滔環保的董事徐湛滔。<br />\n<br />\n原告在入稟狀指，於2018年6至7月，向首被告借出貸款，合共1.8億多元，其中次被告任貸款的擔保人。惟原告指，被告只清還部份利息。<br />\n<br />\n去年9月，次被告向原告開出一張337萬元的支票，作為還款之用。惟原告指，該支票未能兌現。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA1940/2019"},{"pid":"ca39b2baa37ae2f6a20f612b9b014a9dbe9b0d24","tid":1672699,"uid":197121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港資追中資數？"},{"pid":"f4f8719a5939cfba1327f3ee3e1484e36d54d73d","tid":1672699,"uid":164590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:16:21.000Z","msg":"洗米華都反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e6bb4f1962501783169337f210ba12c49037cb","tid":1672699,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca39b2baa37ae2f6a20f612b9b014a9dbe9b0d24","tid":1672699,"uid":197121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港資追中資數？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"同共產黨追數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01e8135b6f3c5b0654e88ea59fe93bce50bae19","tid":1672699,"uid":254504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09: